===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Grimsley (Masters)}}
Grimsley forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Liepard}}, {{p|Sharpedo}}, {{p|Bisharp}}, {{p|Absol}}, and {{p|Honchkrow}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Sharpedo and Absol are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Grimsley became a playable sync pair on November 28, 2019.

